Package com.fssa.projectprovision.model

Class Task

java.lang.Object
com.fssa.projectprovision.model.Task
public class Task extends Object
Represents a Task associated with a project. This class stores information about tasks, including their details, due date, assignee, status, and more.
Author:
JayaprakashJaisankar

      taskCategory - The category of the task.

      taskPriority - The priority of the task.
      taskTags - The tags associated with the task.
